text: George Mastrovich (February 23, 1886 - February 20, 1974) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1886 births Category:1974 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from San Antonio
